                <head>No. 148<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Secretary <persName corresp="#p_AD1">Acheson</persName> visited Bonn May 23–26
                    for discussions with Foreign Secretary <persName corresp="#p_EASA1"
                        >Eden</persName>, Foreign Minister <persName corresp="#p_SR1"
                        >Schuman</persName>, and Chancellor <persName corresp="#p_AK1"
                        >Adenauer</persName> concerning contractual relations and the European
                    Defense Community. For the records of their discussions, see <ref target="#d42"
                        >Documents 42</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
